description: Extension for Bristlecone for modelling plant individuals. An F# library for model-fitting model-selection (MFMS) of ecological models to observational data. The library was developed for individual-based plant modelling using tree ring time-series, but can be used for any ecological models.
releaseNotes:
FEATURE: Configuration options for Filzbach and SA optimisation.
FEATURE: Calculations for day length (sunrise and sunset) built-in to Bristlecone.Dendro.
FEATURE: Calculate confidence intervals using likelihood interval technique.
FEATURE: Standardised formats for loading and saving model-selection results.
summary: Tree ring time-series modelling in F#
title: Bristlecone.Dendro
